      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Ted Summers</b>\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ted-summers-2739a710/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/e/e3/TedSummers.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TedSummers.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ted Summers <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Ted Summers</b>,<br />\nan American information technology and services professional <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, chess amd computer chess aficionado and tester, and active poster in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2007_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://aigames.net/ACCA/ACCAChampionships/ACCA2008Championships/SitePics.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"ACCA2008.JPG\" src=\"/images/e/e7/ACCA2008.JPG\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/ACCA_2008\" title=\"ACCA 2008\">ACCA 2008</a>: <a href=\"/Robert_Hyatt\" title=\"Robert Hyatt\">Bob Hyatt</a>, <a href=\"/Charles_Roberson\" title=\"Charles Roberson\">Charles Roberson</a>, <a href=\"/Pradu_Kannan\" title=\"Pradu Kannan\">Pradu Kannan</a>, <a href=\"/Brian_Richardson\" title=\"Brian Richardson\">Brian Richardson</a> and <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007_...\">2007 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2007 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=14927\">How do you define a clone?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 07, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=14986\">Difference Checker for Clones</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 10, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=16689\">Anthony C's Thoughts on the Zappa Mexico Issue</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 25, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Zappa_versus_Rybka_2007\" title=\"Zappa versus Rybka 2007\">Zappa versus Rybka 2007</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=16732\">Evaluation vs. Search</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 27, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a>, <a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2008</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=19274\">Best Linux Chess Setup</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 29, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19942\">DreamChess 0.2.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 01, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/DreamChess\" title=\"DreamChess\">DreamChess</a>, <a href=\"/Dreamer\" title=\"Dreamer\">Dreamer</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=22490\">Monte Carlo Theory Is it time to Update Comp-Chess Books?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 21, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=22509\">Human Intuition</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 22, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/David_Bronstein\" title=\"David Bronstein\">David Bronstein</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=22546\">Persistent Hash</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/Persistent_Hash_Table\" title=\"Persistent Hash Table\">Persistent Hash Table</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2009</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?t=26401\">Opinions of ChessPartner 6.0</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 05, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/ChessPartner\" title=\"ChessPartner\">ChessPartner</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=28193\">Fortress Draws</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 31, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Fortress\" title=\"Fortress\">Fortress</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=29467\">Djaja study, Big deal! Bright finds the line faster than ... </a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Hans_Secelle#DjajaStudy\" title=\"Hans Secelle\">Djaja Study</a>, <a href=\"/Bright\" title=\"Bright\">Bright</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=29623\">Many to One</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 02, 2009</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=29812\">Free HIARCS Chess Software Programs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/HIARCS\" title=\"HIARCS\">HIARCS</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=30830\">Doch (64-bit Version)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 28, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Doch\" title=\"Doch\">Doch</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=33823\">Problems, problems, problems</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 16, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=38316\">PGN Viewer (Web Browser Plugin)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 07, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=45848\">ChessX Install</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/ChessX\" title=\"ChessX\">ChessX</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=54795\">Android Version of Crafty</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 30, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56124\">SD Syzygy</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy Bases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56602\">Kasparov and thirty years of computer chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 06, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Kasparov_Simul_vs_32_Micros_Hamburg_1985\" title=\"Kasparov Simul vs 32 Micros Hamburg 1985\">Kasparov Simul vs 32 Micros Hamburg 1985</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65515\">Howto turn a DGT3000 into a DGTPi</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/DGT_Pi\" title=\"DGT Pi\">DGT Pi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70721\">The Bryntse Gambit</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 11, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=70835\">Nemeth Gambit Revisited</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 26, 2019 &#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Eduard_Nemeth&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Eduard Nemeth (page does not exist)\">Eduard Nemeth</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71035\">Is Blas, or OpenCL really the right way to go</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ted Summers</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Leela_Chess_Zero#Lc0\" title=\"Leela Chess Zero\">Lc0</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/ted-summers-2739a710/\">Ted Summers | LinkedIn</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/AtlantaChessClub/member/128076132/\">Ted Summers J. - Atlanta Chess Club (Atlanta, GA) | Meetup</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=150270286\">Summers, Ted FIDE Chess Profile</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ted_Summers&amp;action=edit&amp;se